---
// src/components/Features.astro
---

<section class="features">
  <h2>Tools for growth</h2>
  <p class="subtitle">A suite of turn-key solutions for monetizing and growing your app.</p>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-item">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3>Easily customize & ship paywalls</h3>
        <p>Customize one of our native paywall templates or bring your own. Remotely configure changes to any element.</p>
        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn about native paywalls &gt;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-image">
        <img src="/images/paywall.png" alt="Paywall Editor" class="image-main" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-item reverse">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3>Optimize for every audience</h3>
        <p>Tailor how you monetize your app. Target your paywalls, pricing, and packaging by audience segments and in-app placement.</p>
        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn about segmentation with Targeting &gt;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-image">
        <img src="/images/audience1.png" alt="Audience Optimization" class="image-main" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-item">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3>Maximize revenue with A/B testing</h3>
        <p>Learn what drives growth with remotely configurable A/B tests and full-funnel analytics.</p>
        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn about no-code experimentation &gt;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-image">
        <img src="/images/ab.png" alt="A/B Testing" class="image-main" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .feature-item.reverse {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .feature-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .learn-more {
    color: #4f46e5;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .feature-image {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-main {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .image-secondary {
    position: absolute;
    width: 60%;
    bottom: -20%;
    left: -20%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .feature-item, .feature-item.reverse {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-image {
      order: -1;
    }

    .image-secondary {
      position: static;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>